      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Prepare to be amazed! This vehicle is in truly breathtaking, showroom condition. Every detail has been meticulously preserved, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, like-new interior. It drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot\u2014a rare find for any serious collector or enthusiast looking for perfection!",
