    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom-grade condition, reflecting a standard of preservation rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, affirms its status as a premier investment for the discerning driver. Meticulously inspected and maintained to exacting specifications, this vehicle offers an uncompromising driving experience. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate this masterwork of engineering and aesthetic refinement firsthand.",
      "price": 43500.0,
