      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade specimen that defines the term 'mint.' This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its showroom-fresh luster. The exterior paint remains factory-perfect, free of stone chips or swirl marks, and retains a deep, mirror-like finish. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of bolster wear or creasing, and the original factory scent remains. Every switchgear click feels crisp, and the infotainment system functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach\u2014accompanied by a voluminous binder of service records from day one. No leaks, no rattles, and a ride quality that is indistinguishable from the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is not just a used car; it is an investment for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection. Includes both original master keys, the complete toolkit, and all original documentation.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
